ARM: exynos_defconfig: Enable CONFIG_SND_SOC_ODROIDX2 for Odroid-XU3

Enable CONFIG_SND_SOC_ODROIDX2 and CONFIG_SND_SIMPLE_CARD to enable
sound on Odroid-XU3 board using the max98090 audio codec.

